FT  09 MAR 93 / UK Company News: Brit Biotechnology losses increase
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
British Biotechnology Group, the pharmaceutical company, reported losses of
Pounds 3.32m for its third quarter to January 31, against Pounds 1.97m.
