survey by legal recruitment consultants Chambers &amp; Partners. Average salary
for senior in-house lawyers reached Pounds 89,960. The top 10 per cent in
the 30-34 and 40-44 age groups fared better, with remuneration of Pounds
149,000 and Pounds 171,250 respectively.
